data.description: Welcome to your NEW home in McDonough, Georgia! This beautiful 4-bedroom, 3 bathroom house is ready to welcome you with open arms. Situated in an beautifully established neighborhood, this home offers both comfort and convenience to shopping near McDonough & Locust Grove. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a sense of warmth and modernity. The house boasts of beautiful laminate floors, and the kitchen features stainless steel appliances, making meal preparation a breeze and adding a touch of sophistication to your culinary endeavors. Whether you want to relax in your backyard oasis with a concrete pad for barbequing or host gatherings with friends and family, this back yard space offers the perfect setting. No need to worry about staying comfortable during Georgia's hot summers and chilly winters, as this home comes equipped with a recently updated HVAC system. You can enjoy the perfect indoor temperature all year round without any concerns. This move-in ready home means you can start enjoying the perks of homeownership without the hassle of major renovations or repairs. Simply bring your personal belongings and settle into this inviting space. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR NO MONEY DOWN FHA FINANCING! See PRIVATE remarks for more details.
